{"tid":1675264,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家小心加料胡椒噴霧!! 有腐蝕!!","createTime":"2019-10-25T17:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T21:24:45.000Z","uid":299740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab753bcaf82ae463d67686ea94a3701aa9fe1f4","tid":1675264,"uid":299740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"（網民投稿）<br />\n提醒其他手足小心胡椒噴霧<br />\n<br />\n1.呢個並唔係藍色水，而係有合理懷疑佢加左料，狀似胡椒噴霧包裝既不明化學物所造成既傷口，當場救護員亦話從未見過呢種情況，不知係咩物質，只推斷為強鹼性液體。<br />\n<br />\n2.你睇佢表面好似無咩野咁，其實佢表面結左一個好厚既，喺入面仲不停咁腐蝕腐蝕腐蝕緊既，所以其實個傷口係好深，最麻煩就係佢表面已經硬「崛崛」，搽任何藥水呢都滲入唔到去入面...<br />\n<br />\n求醫中，希望平安。希望大家手足小心。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 此帖一出，四方八面手足pm勞工組關心相中手足，仲熱心提供協助，我地都一一轉達了。請各位放心，手足求醫中。齊上齊落，香港人反抗！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHSJ8EF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHSJ8EF.png&h=694ad50a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4d52415d58576274b33b6f917fc576da08c10ee","tid":1675264,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"成個fb都係 唔洗再貼圖"},{"pid":"0d3f1b4e6ef236c081498710581de39d538ea957","tid":1675264,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"上國際 ！！"},{"pid":"a8deaf85cb90a0f5f0e8aefa3330c8f4f26d3fcd","tid":1675264,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T20:05:00.000Z","msg":"好恐怖，好似生化襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134ff060de5a59c9e1cc7224c138944090be92a6","tid":1675264,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T21:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjEwyoq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjEwyoq.gif&h=17384b8c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}